Module 1 Example 1.1: SystemVerilog Class Basics
============================================================

1. Creating base transaction:
   Transaction(id=1, data=0x1234, timestamp=0)
   Transaction ID: 1

2. Creating read transaction (inheritance):
   ReadTransaction(id=2, address=0x1000, data=0xdead)
   Address: 0x1000

3. Creating write transaction (inheritance):
   WriteTransaction(id=3, address=0x2000, data=0xbeef)
   Address: 0x2000

4. Testing copy:
   Original: Transaction(id=1, data=0x1234, timestamp=0)
   Copy:     Transaction(id=1, data=0x1234, timestamp=0)

5. Testing compare:
   txn1 == txn2: 1
   txn1 == read_txn: 0

